
## INTERIOR LIGHT INSPECTION  


1. Remove the interior light. (Refer to 09-18 INTERIOR LIGHT REMOVAL/INSTALLATION.) 
2. Inspect for continuity between the interior light terminals by using an ohmmeter.  

